189
00:12:43,763 --> 00:12:45,731
- Calm down!
- Don't I look calm?!

190
00:12:45,798 --> 00:12:46,565
Hold it, hey!

191
00:12:46,632 --> 00:12:49,001
All a bunch of traitors.

192
00:12:51,771 --> 00:12:53,405
But I won't betray you.

193
