Hey Ryo, gimme a treat.

194
00:13:13,993 --> 00:13:15,127
A treat?

195
00:13:16,228 --> 00:13:17,062
Yeah.

196
00:13:18,130 --> 00:13:21,734
I did a good job, right? So I get a treat.

197
00:13:22,701 --> 00:13:23,869
Treat…

198
00:13:25,404 --> 00:13:31,043
